645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/28\/true-fasting-avoid-sins-vain-talk\/","url_meta":{"origin":24868,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Fasting: True fasting is to avoid sins, vain talk","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sha\u2019bi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cFasting is not merely from food and drink alone. Rather, it is from lies, falsehood, vain talk, and swearing.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 8882 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/23\/siyam-sawm-lies-obscenity-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":24868,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: True fasting is from falsehood and sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, fasting is not only from eating and drinking. Rather, fasting is from vanity and obscenity. If someone abuses you or acts foolish against you, then say: Indeed, I am fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3479\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35803,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/ali-khutbah-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":24868,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Ramadan: Sermon given at the arrival of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sha\u2019bi reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, would deliver a sermon when the month of Ramadan arrived, saying, \u201cThis is the blessed month in which Allah has obligated fasting and not obligated night prayers. Certainly, fasting is not merely from food and drink, but rather from lying, falsehood,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/shield-damaged-gheebah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24868,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sins of tongue damage fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Ubaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield, as long as you do not damage it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2235 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u062c\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24889,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/mujahid-kadhib-ghibah-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":24868,"position":5},"title":"Mujahid on Fasting: Backbiting and lies harm fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Layth reported: Mujahid, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever is safe from two characteristics will secure his fasting: backbiting and falsehood.\u201d Al-Bayhaqi said, \"Just as one guards his fasting from what is not befitting, one must guard himself in the month of Ramadan to obey Allah as much\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-j